HEADWORD: manner name
<hw>manner name</hw> <pos>n.</pos> <fld>(linguistics)</fld> <def>A word
that denotes a manner of doing something; a troponym; as, "march" is a
<ex>manner name</ex> for "walk".</def>⟦br⟧
